Step 1: Final pre-launch check

Review completed phases:
[ ] Docker service deployed and running
[ ] DNS configured and resolving
[ ] Reverse proxy configured (if applicable)
[ ] Monitoring integrated
[ ] Backups configured and tested
[ ] Documentation complete
[ ] All tests passed

